Package: leaflet.extras
Type: Package
Title: Extra functionality for leaflet package.
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Bhaskar", "Karambelkar", email = "bhaskarvk@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Leaflet Javascript library provides many plugins some of which are
  available in the core leaflet package, but there are many more. It is not possible
  to support them all in the core leaflet package. This package serves as an addon to
  the leaflet pacakge by providing extra functionality via leaflet plugins.
License: GPL-3 | file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports: leaflet,
    shiny,
    htmlwidgets,
    htmltools
URL: https://github.com/bhaskarvk/leaflet.extras
BugReports: https://github.com/bhaskarvk/leaflet.extras/issues
